emuInput.TitMainTitle: Boy eating sample wiener on a toothpick with men and women standing behind him at Oswald & Hess Company booth in Syria Mosque for the 1957 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 6, 1957, pg. 18 reads: "5. Miss Willa Rodgers, hostess for the Oswald and Hess Company, served O. and H. samples to delighted homemakers from their booth."
